# endDate

**Instance Property**

The relevant end date.

## Declaration

```swift
var endDate: Date? { get }
```

## Discussion

If the end date isn’t specified when creating the [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INDateRelevanceProvider] object, this property is `nil`.

## Getting the Relevant Dates

- **startDate**: The relevant start date.
